items.name: Devil May Cry Wiki
items.title: Devil May Cry Wiki
items.headline: The Devil May Cry Wiki
items.desc: The Devil May Cry Wiki is a comprehensive database about the Devil May Cry video game series, an action-adventure genre title, originally created by Capcom, and recently rebooted by Ninja Theory. The series focuses on a character named "Dante" who holds a mission of eradicating demons to save the human world from their treacherous attacks. Likewise, this franchise is also extended by the additions of an animated series, cross-over games, and bonus soundtracks.

items.name: Devil May Cry Wiki
items.title: Devil May Cry Wiki
items.headline: Devil May Cry Wiki
items.desc: Devil May Cry Wiki es la enciclopedia en español dedicada a la saga de videojuegos homónima. Este proyecto trata de recopilar toda la información relacionada con estas entregas de acción y beat 'em up desarrolladas por Capcom, donde debes acompañar a Dante en su trabajo como cazarrecompensas.

items.title: Defense Devil Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Defense Devil Wiki
items.desc:
Welcome to the Defense Devil Wiki, a Wiki dedicated to everything about the manga from YOUN In-Wan and YANG Kyung-Il, that anyone can edit. Please help us by creating or editing any of our articles!

Mephisto Bart Kucabara is a devil lawyer. In order to return to the demon world that he was exiled from he needs to collect enough Dark Matter. To do so he creates a plan to claim the Dark Matter from the souls of sinners sentenced to hell. Prove the soul's innocence and the Dark Matter becomes his. But how can he gather enough Dark Matter when his kind personality causes him to continually use it up in order to defend the soul from the Shinigami that has come to take them to hell?

items.name: HiddenShadeVillage Wiki
items.title: HiddenShadeVillage Wiki
items.headline: Get Lost at the Hidden Shade Village Wikia
items.desc: The Hidden Shade Village Wikia community is a community that is dedicated to the preservation of information related to the Hidden Shade Village game. The game is set in a very heavily Naruto inspired world, in a alternative timeline and universe. The game takes place in the not yet recognized village of Hikagakure, meaning Village Hidden in the Shade. The entire premise of the game is to start out as a new shinobi moving to Hikagakure, and players will notice the map, the village and the lore slowly growing, and the players and admins will determine it's pace, and whether or not it reaches renown through their own efforts. Join us on this WIkia if you would like to play the game.

items.name: Devilman Wiki
items.title: Devilman Wiki
items.headline: Learn about Devilman and the demon army!
items.desc: A wiki which homes all information on Go Nagai's brilliant manga series Devilman, its OVA's and many, many spin off's. The story of the original Devilman manga follows the timid teen turned brooding hero Akira Fudo and his eternal battle against Satan and the entire demon race! It was based upon a 39 episode anime series of the first name which itself was based on an early Nagai work called Demon Lord Dante.

items.headline: Welcome to the Makai Ouji:Devils and Realist Wiki!
items.desc: Welcome to Makai Ouji: Devils and Realist Wiki, which is a source of information for the Japanese manga series written by Madoka Takadono and illustrated by Utako Yukihiro. This wiki will also provide information about the anime adaptation that was released in 2013. We welcome all new users to contribute to and edit the wiki!

items.name: Devil Maker: Tokyo Wiki
items.title: Devil Maker: Tokyo Wiki
items.headline: Learn more about Devil Maker: Tokyo
items.desc:
Play a unique RPG card battle game unlike any that have come before! With exciting card battles, a strategic combat system, and outstanding card illustrations, you’re sure to fall in love with Devil Maker: Tokyo!

Sometime in the not-too-distant future, eternal darkness has blanketed Tokyo, and devils from another dimension have taken over the streets. You play as a “contractor,” someone who is able to form contracts with the devils of darkness to try to bring light back to the world. The problem is, your memories only go back 10 years.

Who were you before then? With the help of the devil Yuki and your deck of fearsome devils, battle throughout Tokyo to try to unlock the keys to your past!

items.desc: The Devil Maker: Tokyo Wiki prides itself on being the number one resource for the Android and IOS -based game Devil Maker: Tokyo. The Devil Maker: Tokyo Wiki prides itself on having a complete set of guides that will allow any player to get the help that they need when playing through this guide. Please join us if you would like to help make this wiki a better resource.
